---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="문의하기 | Save Editor Online"
  description="Save Editor Online에 문의하세요. 질문, 지원 및 피드백."
>
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-6xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">문의하기</h1>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
          질문이나 제안이 있거나 인사를 전하고 싶으신가요? 여러분의 의견을 듣고 싶습니다. 아래
          양식을 작성해 주시면 최대한 빨리 답변해 드리겠습니다.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-100 mb-2">응답 시간</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200 text-sm mb-4">
            우리는 소규모 팀이지만 모든 문의에 대해 **24~48시간 이내**에 응답하기 위해 최선을 다하고
            있습니다.
          </p>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-100 mb-2">비즈니스 문의</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200 text-sm">
            파트너십, 언론 또는 비즈니스 문제의 경우 양식에서 "비즈니스 제휴"를 선택하거나 직접
            이메일을 보내주십시오.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl"
            >
              📧
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">이메일</div>
              <a href="mailto:support@saveeditor.top" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline"
                >support@saveeditor.top</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl"
            >
              🐛
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">버그 신고</div>
              <a
                href="https://github.com/paradoxie/saveeditor/issues"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">GitHub Issue 열기</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700"
      >
        <div
          id="success-message"
          class="hidden mb-6 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 text-green-700 px-4 py-3 rounded relative"
          role="alert"
        >
          <strong class="font-bold">메시지 전송됨!</strong>
          <span class="block sm:inline">문의해 주셔서 감사합니다. 곧 연락드리겠습니다.</span>
        </div>
        <form class="space-y-6" id="contact-form">
          <div>
            <label
              for="name"
              class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">이름</label
            >
            <input
              type="text"
              id="name"
              name="name"
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-transparent"
              placeholder="이름"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label
              for="email"
              class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">이메일</label
            >
            <input
              type="email"
              id="email"
              name="email"
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-transparent"
              placeholder="your@email.com"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label
              for="subject"
              class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">제목</label
            >
            <select
              id="subject"
              name="subject"
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-transparent"
            >
              <option value="general">일반 문의</option>
              <option value="support">기술 지원</option>
              <option value="feature">기능 요청</option>
              <option value="bug">버그 신고</option>
              <option value="business">비즈니스 제휴</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label
              for="message"
              class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">메시지</label
            >
            <textarea
              id="message"
              name="message"
              rows="5"
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-transparent"
              placeholder="어떻게 도와드릴까요?"></textarea>
          </div>
          <button
            type="submit"
            class="w-full bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
          >
            <span>메시지 보내기</span>
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                d="M10.894 2.553a1 1 0 00-1.788 0l-7 14a1 1 0 001.169 1.409l5-1.429A1 1 0 009 15.571V11a1 1 0 112 0v4.571a1 1 0 00.725.962l5 1.428a1 1 0 001.17-1.408l-7-14z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script>
    const form = document.getElementById('contact-form') as HTMLFormElement;
    const successMessage = document.getElementById('success-message');

    if (form) {
      form.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
        e.preventDefault();
        // Simulate form submission
        setTimeout(() => {
          form.reset();
          successMessage?.classList.remove('hidden');
          window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' });
        }, 1000);
      });
    }
  </script>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "ContactPage",
      "name": "Save Editor Online 문의",
      "url": "https://saveeditor.top/ko/contact",
      "description": "Save Editor Online 고객 지원 문의."
    }
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
